  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/763a239eb00c651e92ac88b686697559.avif?t=1764106777\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br><br>Cats are wonderful creatures but you better not put them together without proper introduction. So, plan ahead to display them in the right order so they get along!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/da916c56bfaa0343715839a14ae396e5.poster.avif?t=1764106777\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/da916c56bfaa0343715839a14ae396e5.webm?t=1764106777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/da916c56bfaa0343715839a14ae396e5.mp4?t=1764106777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/51c9efd1f0d5fe52404a59ad77f6ad61.avif?t=1764106777\" width=620 height=220 /></span><br><br>When you adopt a cat and there is(are) other(s) cat(s) already living in the house, you need to make a gradual introduction first. Sudocats can be handy in that matter!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/cb5bce580a3a6dc1b6cb740fe72d3298.poster.avif?t=1764106777\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/cb5bce580a3a6dc1b6cb740fe72d3298.webm?t=1764106777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/cb5bce580a3a6dc1b6cb740fe72d3298.mp4?t=1764106777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/6581541c28a3be16bbaa99a4f1db49f5.poster.avif?t=1764106777\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/6581541c28a3be16bbaa99a4f1db49f5.webm?t=1764106777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725640/extras/6581541c28a3be16bbaa99a4f1db49f5.mp4?t=1764106777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Relaxing experience<br>• Classic sudoku with cats<br>• 4x4, 6x6 and 9x9 puzzles<br>• Customizable grid/background<br>• You can change cats/numbers anytime",
